object.script: -- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 150) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 14) -- Draw a 14px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 7) -- Draw a 7px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 2) -- Draw a 2px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawLine(0, h/2, w, h/2) -- Draw a horizontal line through the center of the screen screen.drawLine(w/2, 0, w/2, h) -- Draw a vertical line through the center of the screen end

function onTick() igN=input.getNumber igB=input.getBool cWP=igN(3) Weg=igN(4) Pos=igN(5) KX=igN(6) KY=igN(7) MM=igB(1) SS=igB(2) RR=igB(3) DD=igB(4) end
function onDraw() sW=screen.getWidth() sH=screen.getHeight()
drB(sW-10,2,8,9,MM,"M") drB(sW-10,12,8,9,SS,"S") drB(sW-10,22,8,9,RR,"R") drB(sW-10,32,8,9,DD,"D")
screen.setColor(150,0,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,sH-9,sW-2,7,string.format("%.0f",cWP),1,0) screen.setColor(150,150,150) if Weg >= 1000 then unit = "km" Weg=Weg/1000 else unit = "m" end
screen.drawTextBox(sW/2-18,2,31,9,string.format("%.0f",Weg)..unit,0,0) screen.setColor(255,0,0,155) screen.drawLine(sW/2-1,sH/2,sW/2+2,sH/2) screen.drawLine(sW/2,sH/2-1,sW/2,sH/2+2)
screen.setColor(155,150,150) screen.drawLine(3,4,3,40) screen.setColor(155,0,0) screen.drawRectF(1,Pos-1,5,3)
Zoom=0.050132*1.18842^Pos mX,mY=map.screenToMap(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,3,sH-4)
i=5 for j=0.8,0.95,0.05 do pX,pY=map.mapToScreen(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,mX+10^i-j*10^i,mY) if pX<=sW-10 and pX>=30 then mlen=10^i-j*10^i plen=pX end end i=4 for j=0,0.9,0.1 do pX,pY=map.mapToScreen(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,mX+10^i-j*10^i,mY) if pX<=sW-10 and pX>=30 then mlen=10^i-j*10^i plen=pX end end for i=3,2,-1 do for j=0,0.75,0.25 do pX,pY=map.mapToScreen(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,mX+10^i-j*10^i,mY) if pX<=sW-10 and pX>=30 then mlen=10^i-j*10^i plen=pX end end end i=3 for j=0.8,0.9,0.05 do pX,pY=map.mapToScreen(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,mX+10^i-j*10^i,mY) if pX<=sW-10 and pX>=30 then mlen=10^i-j*10^i plen=pX end end if mlen>=1000 then unit="km" mlen=mlen/1000 else unit="m" end
screen.setColor(150,150,150) screen.drawLine(3,sH-4,plen,sH-4) screen.drawLine(3,sH-5,3,sH-2) screen.drawLine(plen,sH-5,plen,sH-2) screen.drawTextBox(3,sH-10,plen-3,6,string.format("%.0f",mlen)..unit,0,0) end
function drB(x,y,w,l,sta,Bez) screen.setColor(155,155,155) if sta then screen.drawRectF(x,y,w,l) screen.setColor(5,5,5) screen.drawTextBox(x+1,y,w-1,l,Bez,0,0) else screen.drawRect(x,y,w-1,l-1) screen.drawTextBox(x+1,y,w-1,l,Bez,0,0) end end

MM,SS,DD,RR=false,false,false,false move,temp,pulse,safe,init=true,true,true,false,true sW,sH,c,Pos,cWP,Weg,k,Sum=0,0,0,20,0,0,1,0 DX={} DY={} ssC=screen.setColor sdL=screen.drawLine MtS=map.mapToScreen dRF=screen.drawRectF StM=map.screenToMap igN=input.getNumber igB=input.getBool osN=output.setNumber osB=output.setBool function onTick() IP=igB(1) IX=igN(3) IY=igN(4) PX=igN(10) PY=igN(11) MDis=igN(12) MX=igN(13) MY=igN(14) if init or MM then KX=PX KY=PY if KX~=0 and KY~=0 and init then init=false end end if iPIR(IX,IY,1,4,5,36) and IP then Pos=IY end Zoom=0.050132*1.18842^Pos if not MM then if iPIR(IX,IY,0,0,sW,sH) and not iPIR(IX,IY,0,2,7,40) and not iPIR(IX,IY,sW-11,1,10,41) and IP and move then TX,TY=StM(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,IX,IY) tDX=TX-KX tDY=TY-KY move=false elseif not move and c<20 then KX=KX+(tDX)/20 KY=KY+(tDY)/20 c=c+1 elseif c>=20 then KX=TX KY=TY move=true c=0 safe=true end end RR=iPIR(IX,IY,sW-10,22,8,9) and IP DD=iPIR(IX,IY,sW-10,32,8,9) and IP if IP then MM=wec(IX,IY,sW-10,2,8,9,IP,MM) SS=wec(IX,IY,sW-10,12,8,9,IP,SS) else temp=true end if SS and MM and pulse then i=1 while DX[i]~=nil do i=i+1 end DX[i]=MX DY[i]=MY SS=false cWP=cWP+1 elseif not IP then pulse=true end if SS and not MM and pulse and safe then i=1 while DX[i]~=nil do i=i+1 end DX[i]=TX DY[i]=TY safe=false pulse=false cWP=cWP+1 elseif not IP then pulse=true end if RR and pulse and cWP~=0 then i=1 while DX[i]~=nil do i=i+1 end DX[i-1]=nil DY[i-1]=nil pulse=false cWP=cWP-1 elseif not IP then pulse=true end if DD and pulse then for i=1,cWP,1 do DX[i]=nil DY[i]=nil end k=1 cWP=0 Weg=0 elseif not IP then pulse=true end if cWP==0 then AX=PX AY=PY Weg=0 elseif cWP>=k then if DZ(PX,PY,DX[cWP],DY[cWP])>MDis then AX=DX[k] AY=DY[k] if DZ(PX,PY,DX[k],DY[k])<MDis then k=k+1 end end end if cWP<k or DZ(PX,PY,DX[cWP],DY[cWP])<MDis then for i=1,cWP,1 do DX[i]=nil DY[i]=nil end k=1 cWP=0 Weg=0 end if cWP~=0 then for i=k,cWP-1,1 do Sum=Sum+DZ(DX[i],DY[i],DX[i+1],DY[i+1]) end Weg=DZ(PX,PY,DX[k],DY[k])+Sum Sum=0 end osN(1,AX) osN(2,AY) osN(3,cWP) osN(4,Weg) osN(5,Pos) osN(6,KX) osN(7,KY) osB(1,MM) osB(2,SS) osB(3,RR) osB(4,DD) osB(5,iPIR(IX,IY,0,0,sW,sH) and IP) end function onDraw() sW=screen.getWidth() sH=screen.getHeight() ssC(0,0,0) if DX[1]~=nil then SX,SY=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,PX,PY) sdL(SX,SY,MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[k],DY[k])) end j=k+1 while DX[j]~=nil do SX,SY=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[j-1],DY[j-1]) sdL(SX,SY,MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[j],DY[j])) j=j+1 end if cWP>0 then if Pos<25 then ssC(0,0,150) rtx,rty=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[k],DY[k]) dRF(rtx-1,rty-1,3,3) ssC(0,0,0) for i=k+1,cWP-1,1 do rtx,rty=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[i],DY[i]) dRF(rtx-1,rty-1,3,3) end ssC(150,0,0) rtx,rty=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[cWP],DY[cWP]) dRF(rtx-1,rty-1,3,3) else ssC(0,0,150) rtx,rty=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[k],DY[k]) sdL(rtx,rty,rtx+1,rty) ssC(150,0,0) rtx,rty=MtS(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,DX[cWP],DY[cWP]) sdL(rtx,rty,rtx+1,rty) end end end function DZ(cx,cy,dx,dy) return math.sqrt((cx-dx)^2+(cy-dy)^2) end function iPIR(iX,iY,rX,rY,rW,rH) return iX>=rX and iY>=rY and iX<rX+rW and iY<rY+rH end function wec(ix,iy,rX,rY,rW,rH,iP,sta) if iPIR(ix,iy,rX,rY,rW,rH) and sta and temp then sta=false temp=false elseif iPIR(ix,iy,rX,rY,rW,rH) and not sta and temp then sta=true temp=false end return sta end

function onTick() igN=input.getNumber Pos=igN(5) KX=igN(6) KY=igN(7) Zoom=0.050132*1.18842^Pos end
function onDraw() sW=screen.getWidth() sH=screen.getHeight() screen.setMapColorOcean(5,5,5) screen.setMapColorShallows(10,10,10) screen.setMapColorLand(20,20,20) screen.setMapColorGrass(25,25,25) screen.setMapColorSand(30,30,30) screen.setMapColorSnow(50,50,50) screen.drawMap(KX,KY,Zoom)
mLOX,mLOY=map.screenToMap(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,0,0) mRUX,mRUY=map.screenToMap(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,sW,sH) mDis=math.abs(mRUX-mLOX)
for i=5,0,-1 do for j=0,0.75,0.25 do if mDis/(10^i-j*10^i)<=6 and mDis/(10^i-j*10^i)>=2 then mgrid=10^i-j*10^i end end end
pgridX,pgridY=map.mapToScreen(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,mLOX+mgrid,mLOY-mgrid) mLOX=math.floor(mLOX/mgrid)*mgrid mLOY=math.floor(mLOY/mgrid)*mgrid sLOX,sLOY=map.mapToScreen(KX,KY,Zoom,sW,sH,mLOX,mLOY)
screen.setColor(100,100,100,15) for i=sLOX,sW,pgridX do screen.drawLine(i,0,i,sH) end for i=sLOY,sH,pgridY do screen.drawLine(0,i,sW,i) end end

local mxr = 6.25 local h = 0 local w = 0
function onTick() -- Read the touchscreen data from the script's composite input inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
-- Check if the player is pressing the rectangle at (10, 10) with width and height of 20px isPressingRectangleUp = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 0, w, h/2) isPressingRectangleDwn = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, h/2, w, h)
-- Set the composite output, on/off channel 1 output.setNumber(30, mxr * 100)
if isPressingRectangleUp then if mxr < 50 then mxr = (mxr * 2) end end if isPressingRectangleDwn then if mxr > 6.25 then mxr = (mxr / 2) end end end function round(num, numDecimalPlaces) return tonumber(string.format("%." .. (numDecimalPlaces or 0) .. "f", num)) end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() h = screen.getHeight() w = screen.getWidth() screen.setColor(255,255,255) screen.drawText(4,5,round(mxr*100,0)) end

local troll = 0 local s = screen local rej = false local rad = 6.282
function onTick() troll = input.getNumber(9) rej = input.getBool(9) end function tsin(y,r) return (r*math.sin(y)) end function tcos(x,r) return (r*math.cos(x)) end function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() x = w/2 y = h/2 bars(x,y) end function bars(x,y) troll = -troll s.setColor(5,5,5) for i = 0, 5, 1 do s.drawLine((w/6)*i,0,(w/6)*i,h) s.drawLine(0,(h/6)*i,w,(h/6)*i) end s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawRect(0,0,w-1,h-1) if rej == false then s.drawLine(x+tcos(troll*rad,w/8),y+tsin(troll*rad,w/8),x+tcos(troll*rad,w/4),y+tsin(troll*rad,w/4)) s.drawLine(x-tcos(troll*rad,w/8),y-tsin(troll*rad,w/8),x-tcos(troll*rad,w/4),y-tsin(troll*rad,w/4)) end end

-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawClear() screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(0, 0, w, h, "Loading", 0, 0) screen.drawRect(0+10, 38, w-20, 5) screen.drawRectF(0+11, 39, loadb, 5)
end

temp1 = input.getNumber(2)
t1 = input.getNumber(3) bar= (t1/1)*(-12)

end

screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawRect(0, 0, 32, 63) screen.drawRect(32, 0, 31, 63)

screen.drawRect(7, 44, 3, 12) screen.drawRectF(7, 57, 3, bar)
screen.drawRect(36, 44, 3, 12) screen.drawRectF(36, 57, 3, bar1)

function onDraw() ssC(0,0,0) screen.drawClear()
ssC(200,200,200) screen.drawRectF(0,0,32,7)
ssC(0,0,0) dTB(1,0,32,7,"We",-1,0) dTB(10,0,32,7,"a",-1,0) dTB(14,0,32,7,"t",-1,0) dTB(18,0,32,7,"he",-1,0) dTB(27,0,32,7,"r",-1,0)
ssC(200,200,200) dL(9,0,9,7) dL(26,0,26,7)
dTB(1,7,32,7,"T",-1,0) dTB(4,7,32,7,":",-1,0) dTB(0,7,24,7,string.format("%.0f",Temperatur),1,0) dTB(0,7,31,7,"C",1,0) dL(25,8,25,9)

if Timer < 4 then page = 1 elseif Timer >= 4 and Timer < 8 then page = 2 elseif Timer >= 8 then Timer = 0 end if page == 1 then Anzeige(20,14,WindG/39) ssC(200,200,200) elseif page == 2 then WindRichtung(Kompass,WindR) end Timer = Timer+1/60

function Farbe(i) if i==0 then ssC(0, 255, 0) elseif i==1 then ssC(9, 246, 0) elseif i==2 then ssC(23, 222, 0) elseif i==3 then ssC(47, 208, 0) elseif i==4 then ssC(81, 130, 0) elseif i==5 then ssC(128, 128, 0) elseif i==6 then ssC(130, 81, 0) elseif i==7 then ssC(208, 47, 0) elseif i==8 then ssC(222, 23, 0) elseif i==9 then ssC(246, 9, 0) elseif i==10 then ssC(255, 0, 0) end end
function Anzeige(x,y,Wert) for i = 0, 10, 1 do if Wert >= (i/11) then Farbe(i) dL(x+i, y, x+i, y+5) end end end
function WindRichtung(C,WR) Temp = C-WR if C-WR<-0.5 then Temp = 0.5-(WR-C-0.5) elseif C-WR >0.5 then Temp = -0.5+(WR-C+0.5) end if (Temp) > -0.0625 and (Temp) < 0.0625 then TEXT = "N" elseif (Temp) > 0.0625 and (Temp) < 0.1875 then TEXT = "NW" elseif (Temp) > -0.1875 and (Temp) < -0.0625 then TEXT = "NE" elseif (Temp) > 0.4375 or (Temp) < -0.4375 then TEXT = "S" elseif (Temp) > 0.3125 and (Temp) < 0.4375 then TEXT = "SW" elseif (Temp) > -0.4375 and (Temp) < -0.3125 then TEXT = "SE" elseif (Temp) > 0.1875 and (Temp) < 0.3125 then TEXT = "W" elseif (Temp) > -0.3125 and (Temp) < -0.1875 then TEXT = "E" end ssC(200,200,200) dTB(0,13,31,7,TEXT,1,0) end
